},{"pid":"7331ba252bfa937b96f6cfbf186e50c7d06eaf2c","tid":170541,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T23:23:44.000Z","msg":"老解要影有咩咁奇 .. 咁都係新聞?<br />\n重有偏偏係熱時知道, 又搵得齊幾多隻.<br />\n<br />\n可能熱時搭晒線知道大陸係香港既通訊.<br />\n<br />\n真係熱血狗仔囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7933ed918c9ff13f25c72bb3bb0fceaae1f8fa1f","tid":170541,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T23:35:35.000Z","msg":"咁嚴格上黎講又唔算干預既，最多咪睇下熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其實係軍營攞支望遠鏡一樣睇到"},{"pid":"d57ee3f38deb833075e31b17b6f0f70492e4afb1","tid":170541,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:22:18.000Z","msg":"有圖有真相？"},{"pid":"b23461ed85ceace20c3b8484ef80274ee07a55e5","tid":170541,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:28:47.000Z","msg":"課金的功課 可惜香港已死"},{"pid":"a191095474816b7e0ac3836779a87c5b6ed25fa9","tid":170541,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:48:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢地點收到料？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次李家三父子入中聯辦見張曉明又畀佢地獨家影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要熱狗影呢啲野對中共有咩好處</blockquote><br />\n比個訊息出黎：<br />\n支共要監視薯片<br />\n即係佢無得到中央認同"},{"pid":"3764a0a79efbc658fac3993f76ebca0df0e9b8e2","tid":170541,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:55:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"720480686b3600d6736bbaf2e3103f9947a43c0a","tid":170541,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗時報只係大公文匯之流</blockquote><br />\n只有蘋果才是清泉 不偏不倚 鼓勵市民參與小圈子選舉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63ebee8b937cad819b08f318a4093700814f621","tid":170541,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep